Class BlockTransmitter

java.lang.Object
  freenet.io.xfer.BlockTransmitter

public class BlockTransmitter
extends Object

Author:
ian Given a PartiallyReceivedBlock retransmit to another node (to be received by BlockReceiver). Since a PRB can be concurrently transmitted to many peers NOWHERE in this class is prb.abort() to be called.
